<p>FTX was founded by Sam Bankman-Fried in 2017 with the goal to "develop a platform robust enough for professional trading firms and intuitive enough for first-time users". FTX provides access to trading Crypto, tokenized Equities, and Bitcoin Options for clients outside of the <a rel="nofollow" target="_blank" href="https://help.ftx.com/hc/en-us/articles/360042412652-Location-Restrictions-">restricted locations</a> with no minimum deposit. FTX also provides a platform-native FTT token, an NFT marketplace, and margin borrowing services.</p>